{"tid":1747363,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"咪撚再講非黑即白 現實就係咁","createTime":"2019-11-23T07:39:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-23T07:55:35.000Z","uid":102491,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"9b4d041cf06d26b087081542ed88db12771b1981","tid":1747363,"uid":102491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T07:39:26.000Z","msg":"見到啲叫人投白票既post會話點解要非黑即白 點解唔投建制就一要定要投泛民<br />\n<br />\n我依家答你點解<br />\n因為<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我要建制輸</span></span> 投白票等於建制多個機會贏<br />\n對家吹風吹到咁勁 又有得種票 又有班死廢老藍絲 你仲同我講唔投泛民？<br />\n<br />\n事實就係咁 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">你唔投泛民 建制贏既機會就大啲</span> 係非黑即白嫁喇 一係建制當選 一係泛民 一係就本土 自己諗下 想要建制定係泛民啦"},{"pid":"eec103bc7ab1c53684279dd1fa29fe071144f3a7","tid":1747363,"uid":102491,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T07:42:49.000Z","msg":"非黑即白？<br />\n你唔投只會令建制更容易贏<br />\n你唔投只會令我地少左一票<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔係你唔投就冇左個選舉結果 你唔投佢一樣會出結果 係令建制贏既結果</span> 自己諗下啦"},{"pid":"7353db02c1956c3afcdf60c000701b713f74f4a1","tid":1747363,"uid":102491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T07:43:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c4adeb015b8a38861100fe2fa97ff33c00ebdc8b","tid":1747363,"uid":102491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T07:43:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1914b291a1ebf3a311c4525a96a0b738b8f9dcab","tid":1747363,"uid":62721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T07:43:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ddfa9d812aa059e10f6f4ebb28f147d8b3e195bd","tid":1747363,"uid":288312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T07:45:17.000Z","msg":"[深度數據分析] 你知道嗎？多你一票好多<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ezEbiS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ezEbiS</a>"},{"pid":"8b96ca8396ca9c5b78a51f1f07384aae83ce6643","tid":1747363,"uid":21279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T07:45:48.000Z","msg":"你有